    BOp, IPropertySet, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class Union
extends AbstractSubqueryOp
    UNION()[maxParallel(default all); subqueries=ops] 
     UNION([],{subqueries=[a,b,c]})
    Will run the subqueries a, b, and c in parallel for each source IBindingSet. The output of those subqueries will be routed to the UNION operator (their parent).
